text:
Claudia Hernández Aguila (born 9 January 1997) is a Cuban volleyball player.
She played at the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2017 FIVB U23 Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship.
She played for La Habana.
